{"name":"Heavy","content":"<p>Requires a minimum Strength score of 15. Creatures with a Strength score lower than 15 have disadvantage on attack rolls with heavy weapons as its size and bulk is to cumbersome to use effectively.</p>","folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"sokvEf9kzud7HpGx":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"JournalEntry.o9ExdoTQZbl9oMz9"}},"_id":"07VlakQgG3OMkBr6"}
{"name":"Thrown","content":"<p>If a weapon has the thrown property, you can throw the weapon to make a ranged attack. If the weapon is a melee weapon, you use the same ability modifier for that attack roll and damage roll that you would use for a melee attack with the weapon.</p>","folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"sokvEf9kzud7HpGx":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"JournalEntry.SF5Lubbip43P6B3u"}},"_id":"0bFz3wW5Wv08ECWO"}
{"name":"Light","content":"<p>A light weapon is small and easy to handle, making it ideal for use when fighting with two weapons.</p>","folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"sokvEf9kzud7HpGx":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"JournalEntry.g0SQojBKqX00ymfD"}},"_id":"4ggmCH7ltSznwNdG"}
{"name":"Special","content":"<p>A weapon with the special property has unusual rules governing its use explained in the weapon notes. Additionally, special weapons cannot be improved by weapon mods.</p>","folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"sokvEf9kzud7HpGx":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"JournalEntry.Cmv83BF4NKoMwG9O"}},"_id":"6jTTmoGWPaCpiHQa"}
{"name":"Recoil","content":"<p>A weapon with the Recoil property generates a lot of kickback when fired. You use your choice of your Strength or Dexterity modifier for the attack and damage rolls. You must use the same modifier for both rolls.</p>","folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"sokvEf9kzud7HpGx":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"JournalEntry.3LQFsPTLqjp7O3Js"}},"_id":"EsgmtnHIpii8GH2Y"}
{"_id":"F7QgH7iYDJvhgV12","name":"Double Tap","content":"<p>When you make a ranged attack with this weapon, you can use your bonus action to make a second ranged attack. You do not add your ability modifier to the damage of the bonus attack, unless that modifier is negative. The second attack may be on the same or a different target.</p>","folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"sokvEf9kzud7HpGx":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"JournalEntry.LmNfJe6mLKTj7Ere"}}}
{"_id":"G98GCouqApwEgC2f","name":"Two-Handed","content":"<p>This weapon requires two hands when you attack with it. Takes up 2 weapon slots.</p>","folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"sokvEf9kzud7HpGx":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"JournalEntry.0piH10Cj420pIL0I"}}}
{"_id":"HOKCiJvtALi2bBGf","name":"Finesse","content":"<p>When making an attack with a finesse weapon, you use your choice of your Strength or Dexterity modifier for the attack and damage rolls. You must use the same modifier for both rolls.</p>","folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"sokvEf9kzud7HpGx":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"JournalEntry.WDCvIX6l86AspHmI"}}}
{"name":"Hip Fire","content":"<p><span style=\"color:rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7);font-family:Roboto, sans-serif;letter-spacing:0.25px;background-color:#1e1e1e\">When making a ranged attack on a target creature within </span><span style=\"background-repeat:no-repeat;box-sizing:inherit;padding:0px;margin:0px;color:rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7);font-family:Roboto, sans-serif;letter-spacing:0.25px;background-color:#1e1e1e\" data-v-64729cc4>2 meters</span><span style=\"color:rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7);font-family:Roboto, sans-serif;letter-spacing:0.25px;background-color:#1e1e1e\">, you do not have disadvantage on the attack roll.</span></p>","folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"sokvEf9kzud7HpGx":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"JournalEntry.X2JVvKC2GqKgaUKb"}},"_id":"O268JyImqQvuTHzD"}
{"name":"Burst Fire","content":"<p>This weapon can be used to make a normal single-target attack, or can be used to target a 4-meter cube within its normal range. Each creature in the area must succeed on a DC 15 Dexterity saving throw or suffer the weapon's normal damage. This action uses 3 heat.</p>","folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"sokvEf9kzud7HpGx":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"JournalEntry.jUnOuUA266ylXWID"}},"_id":"RhssSY9ASxXrYB9G"}
{"name":"Arc","content":"<p>Deals lightning damage. On a hit, deals half of the damage dealt to 1 additional creature within 2 meters of the hit target. If there is more than one creature within 2 meters of the initial target, choose the second target randomly.</p>","folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"sokvEf9kzud7HpGx":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"JournalEntry.Va6GmnuEouC52ogk"}},"_id":"dzSjkrzfe6htuhoo"}
{"_id":"h0saRaAHhMQMhAZ3","name":"Versatile","content":"<p>This weapon can be used with one or two hands. A damage value in parentheses appears with the property--the damage when the weapon is used with two hands to make a melee attack.</p>","folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"sokvEf9kzud7HpGx":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"JournalEntry.vSBVBJj6b2Tp6ukl"}}}
{"name":"Silent","content":"<p>Makes no noise when used to make an attack roll</p>","folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"sokvEf9kzud7HpGx":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"JournalEntry.qDfjUXNdHqEC0dD8"}},"_id":"xOS7MekXvgaHXCTy"}
